---
import Wrapper from "@components/ui/Wrapper.astro";
---

<Wrapper>
  <div
    class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-white py-24 sm:py-32 lg:overflow-visible "
  >
    <div
      class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start lg:gap-y-10"
    >
      <div
        class="lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-1 lg:mx-auto lg:grid lg:w-full lg:max-w-7xl lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-8 lg:px-8"
      >
        <div class="lg:pr-4">
          <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
            <h2
              class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl"
            >
              Your Smooth Move Starts Here
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-700">
              Take the stress out of moving with All Nepal Packers and Movers
              streamlined approach.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="-ml-12 -mt-12 p-12 lg:sticky lg:top-4 lg:col-start-2 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-start-1 lg:overflow-hidden"
      >
        <img
          class="w-[48rem] max-w-none bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-400/10 sm:w-[57rem]"
          src="./moving_01.svg"
          alt="Mover is carrying a box"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-2 lg:mx-auto lg:grid lg:w-full lg:max-w-7xl lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-8 lg:px-8"
      >
        <div class="lg:pr-4">
          <div class="max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-700 lg:max-w-lg">
            <p>
              Moving shouldn't be a source of worry. We understand the
              importance of a smooth and hassle-free relocation. That's why
              we've created a clear, step-by-step process that guides you from
              your initial inquiry to settling comfortably in your new home.
            </p>
            <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  viewBox="0 0 36 36"
                  ><path
                    fill="currentColor"
                    d="m33 6.4l-3.7-3.7a1.71 1.71 0 0 0-2.36 0L23.65 6H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v22a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h22a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V11.76l3-3a1.67 1.67 0 0 0 0-2.36M18.83 20.13l-4.19.93l1-4.15l9.55-9.57l3.23 3.23ZM29.5 9.43L26.27 6.2l1.85-1.85l3.23 3.23Z"
                    class="clr-i-solid clr-i-solid-path-1"></path><path
                    fill="none"
                    d="M0 0h36v36H0z"></path></svg
                >
                <span
                  ><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900"
                    >Initial Consultation</strong
                  > Reach out to us for a free, no-obligation quote. Weâ€™ll gather
                  all the essential details about your move. For precise estimates,
                  we can conduct an in-home survey to assess the volume and specific
                  needs.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M10 1a4.5 4.5 0 00-4.5 4.5V9H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.5V5.5A4.5 4.5 0 0010 1zm3 8V5.5a3 3 0 10-6 0V9h6z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span
                  ><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900"
                    >Customized Moving Plan</strong
                  > We create a personalized moving plan based on your requirements,
                  including packing services and special handling. We establish a
                  convenient moving date and timeline to minimize disruption to your
                  life or business.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  viewBox="0 0 640 512"
                  ><path
                    fill="currentColor"
                    d="M256 48c0-26.5 21.5-48 48-48h288c26.5 0 48 21.5 48 48v416c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H381.3c1.8-5 2.7-10.4 2.7-16V253.3c18.6-6.6 32-24.4 32-45.3v-32c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48H256zm315.3 299.3c6.2-6.2 6.2-16.4 0-22.6l-64-64c-6.2-6.2-16.4-6.2-22.6 0l-64 64c-6.2 6.2-6.2 16.4 0 22.6s16.4 6.2 22.6 0l36.7-36.7V432c0 8.8 7.2 16 16 16s16-7.2 16-16V310.6l36.7 36.7c6.2 6.2 16.4 6.2 22.6 0M0 176c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h352c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16v32c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16H16c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16zm352 80v224c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32H64c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32V256zm-208 64c-8.8 0-16 7.2-16 16s7.2 16 16 16h96c8.8 0 16-7.2 16-16s-7.2-16-16-16z"
                  ></path></svg
                >
                <span
                  ><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900"
                    >Packing and Preparation</strong
                  > Our team uses high-quality materials to securely pack your belongings,
                  labeling all boxes for easy unpacking. We offer disassembly services
                  for larger items, ensuring safe transportation and reassembly at
                  your new location.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  viewBox="0 0 640 512"
                  ><path
                    fill="currentColor"
                    d="M64 32C28.7 32 0 60.7 0 96v304c0 44.2 35.8 80 80 80c26.2 0 49.4-12.6 64-32c14.6 19.4 37.8 32 64 32c44.2 0 80-35.8 80-80c0-5.5-.6-10.8-1.6-16h163.2c-1 5.2-1.6 10.5-1.6 16c0 44.2 35.8 80 80 80s80-35.8 80-80c0-5.5-.6-10.8-1.6-16h1.6c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32v-90.3c0-9.2-3.2-18.2-9-25.3l-58.8-71.8c-10.6-13-26.5-20.5-43.3-20.5H480V96c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64zm521 224H480v-64h48.8c2.4 0 4.7 1.1 6.2 2.9zm-57 112a32 32 0 1 1 0 64a32 32 0 1 1 0-64m-352 32a32 32 0 1 1 64 0a32 32 0 1 1-64 0m-96-32a32 32 0 1 1 0 64a32 32 0 1 1 0-64"
                  ></path></svg
                >
                <span
                  ><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900"
                    >Moving Day</strong
                  >
                  Our team arrives on time and handles the loading process with care,
                  using modern equipment for safe handling. Your belongings are transported
                  in our well-maintained, secure trucks to ensure they arrive safely.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  viewBox="0 0 512 512"
                  ><path
                    fill="currentColor"
                    d="M61.39 25.39C93.9 58.33 115.8 96.55 133.3 134.5c4.9-12 7.3-22.2 18.9-32.3c47 26.5 60.3 43.3 64.4 80.4h66.8c1.8-36 7.6-56.3 36.5-82.81c15.9 12.41 20 26.91 28.1 40.71c8.5-38.9 37.3-81.28 76.7-101.89c-52.5-11.56-108.5-.43-153.3 17.54c9.3 6.39 22.7 11.23 26.9 19.5c-19 9.79-39.5 42.35-51.2 69.35c-14.1-25.1-43.5-53.44-72-67.64c11.5-11.58 23-15.79 34.5-22.89C176.6 36.1 117.5 27 61.39 25.39m8.85 175.21l-41.25 110H137.8l41.2-110zm134.76 0l41.2 110H483l-41.2-110zm-22 40.6l-32.8 87.4H73v158h110zm18 0v245.4h238v-158H233.8z"
                  ></path></svg
                >
                <span
                  ><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900"
                    >Unloading and Setup</strong
                  >
                  Upon arrival, we carefully unload your items and place them in
                  designated rooms as per your instructions. We reassemble any disassembled
                  items and assist with the initial setup to make your new place
                  functional.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg
                  class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  ><path
                    fill="currentColor"
                    d="M3 23v-7q0-2.075 1.463-3.537T8 11h1V3q0-.825.588-1.412T11 1h2q.825 0 1.413.588T15 3v8h1q2.075 0 3.538 1.463T21 16v7zm2-2h2v-3q0-.425.288-.712T8 17t.713.288T9 18v3h2v-3q0-.425.288-.712T12 17t.713.288T13 18v3h2v-3q0-.425.288-.712T16 17t.713.288T17 18v3h2v-5q0-1.25-.875-2.125T16 13H8q-1.25 0-2.125.875T5 16z"
                  ></path></svg
                >
                <span
                  ><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900"
                    >Post-Move Support</strong
                  >
                  We take care of any packing materials and debris, leaving your
                  new place clean and tidy. Our team conducts survey to ensure everything
                  went smoothly and to address any additional needs.</span
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-8">
              Now that you've seen our clear moving process, you can move with
              confidence! Contact All Nepal Packers and Movers today and let us
              take the stress out of your relocation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Wrapper>
